Screenslop is inspired by Pixelslop and the practical need to review Apple app UI from real runtime evidence.

Pixelslop: https://github.com/gabelul/pixelslop
Baguette: https://github.com/tddworks/baguette
XcodeBuildMCP: https://github.com/cameroncooke/XcodeBuildMCP

No upstream source text is copied into the runtime scaffold beyond ordinary command and project references. If future versions port licensed prose or code, attribution should be added here with file-level detail.
